artificialFastqGenerator

Class ArtificialFastqGenerator.BabyRead

  • java.lang.Object
    • artificialFastqGenerator.AbstractRead
      • artificialFastqGenerator.ArtificialFastqGenerator.BabyRead
  • Enclosing class:
    ArtificialFastqGenerator

    public class ArtificialFastqGenerator.BabyRead
extends AbstractRead
    A sequence of nucleobases which may be used to create a read. Has fields for (1) the sequence, (2) the index in the ArrayList nucleobases of the first nucleobase to prohibit read generation, either due to its target coverage constraint or the readsContainingN filter. A failure index of -1 means there was no failure.

    mframpton
